{"tid":1830093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[春袋]狗方腰斬集會，反對遊行解決方案","createTime":"2020-01-19T10:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T12:12:38.000Z","uid":335967,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"58c8e7ff5fc89e143679210d86d6504fb46a07ed","tid":1830093,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"幾乎每次狗方都係遊行途中強行腰斬， 一係就反對遊行，只批集會，途中衝入嚟拉手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到越嚟越少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解決方法就係每個禮拜都申請一次喺元朗舉行追究721遊行</span></span>，追究警黑合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申請嘅目的並唔係叫手足送頭，而係:<br />\n1. 元朗嘅鄉黑一定會出聲反對<br />\n2. 警方一定會出反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n當每個禮拜都申請+不斷宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而警方每個禮拜都反對， 就係警黑合作最好嘅文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">亦可以聲東擊西</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要每個禮拜都申請，文宣要接近民陣遊行嘅規模<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"efea6efa56f7e0b1824b21fe3a098c1f80cb5810","tid":1830093,"uid":335967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"3a46943c46b9e3464976c16fee370d2575ccebdf","tid":1830093,"uid":270281,"like"